### Review System - Example API Calls
### Use these with REST Client extension or Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get all reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get all reviews for a specific tour
GET {{baseUrl}}/tours/TOUR_ID_HERE/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Create a review (user only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "review": "This tour was absolutely amazing! The guide was knowledgeable and the scenery was breathtaking.",
  "rating": 5,
  "tour": "TOUR_ID_HERE"
}

### 4. Create a review via nested route
POST {{baseUrl}}/tours/TOUR_ID_HERE/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "review": "Great experience, would definitely recommend to friends and family!",
  "rating": 4
}

### 5. Get a specific review
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/REVIEW_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Update your own review
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reviews/REVIEW_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "review": "Updated: This tour exceeded all my expectations!",
  "rating": 5
}

### 7. Delete your own review
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reviews/REVIEW_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get a tour with its reviews populated
GET {{baseUrl}}/tours/TOUR_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
